The numbers in front of the tracks are the play order.

001 (Jamrock) was listed at #100 and 100 (Crazy) was listed at #1. They are labelled this way so you go from:

100th best, 99th, 98th ... 3rd, 2nd, best

when played (at least that's the idea - hope it works for you).
